{"tid":1266190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因政府基於安全及保安理由，要求會展於6月30日（星期日）關閉場地","createTime":"2019-06-29T13:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T16:23:06.000Z","uid":266569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96bea65803a57fb981a989af594f0e6712808fba","tid":1266190,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"原訂於6月28至30日，一連三日於會展舉行的「優質寵物用品展 2019」，因政府基於安全及保安理由，要求會展於6月30日（星期日）關閉場地。寵物展將提前於今日6月29日（星期六）晚上9時結束。原訂於6月30日（星期日）於會場舉辦的展覽及各項活動亦將取消。作為主辦機構的展覽集團，對有關決定感到非常無奈。<br />\n<br />\n係Facebook 見到d人嬲到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awY4FTL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawY4FTL.jpg&h=78a24867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqdwkTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqdwkTM.jpg&h=1703729b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/232205140315748/posts/1178552219014364/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F232205140315748%2Fposts%2F1178552219014364%2F&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo8tNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=c95f26e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/232205140315748/posts/1178552219014364/</a>"},{"pid":"51e41e5adf1f867cd03121c534147b3e07b8e85f","tid":1266190,"uid":66283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"絲打唔好做傻事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}